PN,43901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FA devastated Devon family is calling
OL,7,Ffor tougher penalties for people
OL,8,Fconvicted of "one-punch" manslaughters
OL,9,Fafter discovering that their son's
OL,10,Fkiller could be released in as little
OL,11,Fas 17 months.
OL,13,FCemal Yilmaz died just before
OL,14,FChristmas last year, three days after
OL,15,Fbeing assaulted in Exmouth on a night
OL,16,Fout. He was punched from behind by a
OL,17,Fnewly qualified Royal Marine, Joseph
OL,18,FJones, who told others that the
OL,19,Fpopular 6ft2 man had disrespected him
OL,20,Fby asking if he came from Birmingham.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FJones pleaded guilty to manslaughter
OL,7,Flast month and was sentenced by the
OL,8,Fjudge to three years and four months.
OL,9,FCemal's family appealed against the
OL,10,Fleniency of the sentence, but that was
OL,11,Fturned down.
OL,13,FHowever, his parents were not
OL,14,Finitially told of the decision.
OL,15,FInstead, a letter went to Cemal's
OL,16,Faunt. The family say they feel they
OL,17,Fhave been let down at every turn by
OL,18,Fthe justice system, and that they have
OL,19,Fhad no contact at all from the Royal
OL,20,FMarines about the actions of one of
OL,21,Ftheir own.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FCemal's mother, Ann-Marie Yilmaz,
OL,7,Fdescribed the moment she saw her son
OL,8,Fin hospital after the fatal punch.
OL,10,FShe said: "The bleed was that big in
OL,11,Fhis brain. He had a broken jaw, a
OL,12,Ffracture to the back of his skull and
OL,13,Fhe was bleeding from his right ear. I
OL,14,Fjust couldn't believe it. I just
OL,15,Fscreamed and then they put him on life
OL,16,Fsupport machine because we couldn't
OL,17,Faccept it. We couldn't accept losing
OL,18,Fhim."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FThat punch had devastating
OL,7,Fconsequences. There was no argument
OL,8,Fthat preceded it - Joseph Jones hit
OL,9,FCemal as he turned away, breaking his
OL,10,Fjaw and causing him to smash his head
OL,11,Fon the pavement. Cemal died at
OL,12,FDerriford Hospital three days later.
OL,14,FIn court last month, Jones pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to manslaughter. Describing the
OL,16,Fattack on Cemal as a moment of
OL,17,Fmadness, the judge sentenced him to
OL,18,Fjust three years and four months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FThe judge told the court that Jones
OL,7,Fwould be eligible for release after
OL,8,Fserving two thirds of his sentence.
OL,9,FThe family were later notified that
OL,10,Fthis was incorrect and that he could
OL,11,Fbe freed as soon as 17 months. They
OL,12,Fnow believe Jones is in an open prison.
OL,14,FCemal's father, Ozkan Yilmaz, told ITV
OL,15,FWest Country: "He killed my son. He's
OL,16,Fa very dangerous person, He's very,
OL,17,Fvery dangerous. He's not a person,
OL,18,Fhe's an evil being, you know, he
OL,19,Fkilled my son for no reason. How can
OL,20,Fhe be in an open prison?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FAnn-Marie explained: "So we were
OL,7,Fthinking, right, brilliant ok, he's
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty and then the next
OL,9,Fminute, we were told that he's got
OL,10,Fthis lenient sentence, that we all sat
OL,11,Fin court and listened to. I couldn't
OL,12,Fbelieve it. I couldn't believe it,
OL,13,Fwhat was said. 'His brain wasn't
OL,14,Fmature enough, he had a moment of
OL,15,Fmadness.' And I had to get up and walk
OL,16,Fout of court because I was so - I was
OL,17,Fjust shocked. I was in shock."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FOzkan said: "We don't want any other
OL,7,Fpeople to lose their brother, son,
OL,8,Fsister, you know whatever, member of
OL,9,Ftheir family or friend. That happened
OL,10,Fto us, our heart is bleeding 24/7.
OL,11,FThat evil being took my backbone from
OL,12,Fme. Cem was my everything. He was my
OL,13,Fsolid backbone. He took that away from
OL,14,Fme for no reason."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FAnn-Marie added: "I don't do anything
OL,7,Freally, I just sit and I just think
OL,8,Fabout Cem 24/7. And I have visions of
OL,9,FCem, how I saw him in hospital. And
OL,10,Fthe anger that I feel towards this
OL,11,FJoseph Jones will never go away. The
OL,12,Fsentences are just horrendous what
OL,13,Fthey are giving people. It's pittance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FOzkan agreed: "My son didn't have a
OL,7,Fchance to protect himself, because he
OL,8,Fdidn't see the dangers - because there
OL,9,Fwas no argument. Nothing. He just
OL,10,Fasked him if he was from Birmingham.
OL,11,FAnd he turned around, talking with his
OL,12,Ffriend and next minute that evil,
OL,13,Fcowardly - from behind, he gave my son
OL,14,Fa killer punch."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FAnn-Marie said: "The pain that we are
OL,7,Fgoing through is just horrendous. And
OL,8,FI wouldn't wish this on any family,
OL,9,Fany mother, any father, any brother,
OL,10,Fany sister. There needs to be harsher
OL,11,Fsentences put in place because of
OL,12,Fthis. Because people like us, we just
OL,13,Fdon't know what to do. We don't know
OL,14,Fwhat to do. He's all right - 17 months
OL,15,Fdown the line he's going to be out,
OL,16,Fhe's going to be with his family, he's
OL,17,Fgoing to be celebrating his
OL,18,FChristmases and all that. We've got no-
OL,19,Fone. We've got no Cem."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FShe added: "I find it very difficult
OL,7,Fbecause I can't go past the place
OL,8,Fwhere he fell. The memories are there.
OL,9,FAnd when I go into town, it's lovely
OL,10,Fand the people are lovely, but I'm
OL,11,Fwaiting for Cem to walk past. Because
OL,12,Fthat's what he used to do, he'd see us
OL,13,Fin town and he'd wave, and he'd come
OL,14,Fover: 'Hiya mum, you alright?' He was
OL,15,Fbrilliant, he was brilliant. He was my
OL,16,Fbaby. And I'm going to miss him. So
OL,17,Fmuch."
OL,19,FMore than 500 people were at Cemal's
OL,20,Ffuneral earlier this year. His family
OL,21,Fsay he was loved by all who knew him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice said: "This
OL,7,Fwas a tragic crime and we express our
OL,8,Fsincere condolences to the family and
OL,9,Ffriends of Cemal Yilmaz.
OL,11,F"Victims deserve the support they need
OL,12,Fto rebuild their lives and we're
OL,13,Freviewing how we can make it easier
OL,14,Ffor them to raise concerns about
OL,15,Foffender's licence conditions.
OL,17,F"Prisoners are only moved to open
OL,18,Fjails after a careful risk assessment
OL,19,Fand must obey strict rules to remain
OL,20,Fthere."
OL,26,@nD@_OUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780081925
OL,3,CRoyal Marine who killed man with one
OL,4,Cpunch could be released in 17 months
OL,6,FOn behalf of the Royal Marines, a
OL,7,FRoyal Navy spokesperson said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with the family and
OL,9,Ffriends of Cemal Yilmaz following this
OL,10,Ftragic incident.
OL,12,F"We hold our people in the highest
OL,13,Fstandards and will take appropriate
OL,14,Faction, including dismissal from the
OL,15,FRoyal Navy, against anyone who fails
OL,16,Fto uphold these high standards."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
